# Incident Post-Mortem Reports

This directory contains post-mortem documentation for production incidents.

**File Naming Convention:** `YYYY-MM-DD-incident-short-title.md`

**Example:** `2025-10-15-matching-system-outage.md`

**Purpose:** 
- Historical record of incidents
- Learning resource for team
- Reference for preventing repeat issues

See `docs/INCIDENT_RESPONSE.md` for post-mortem template.
